---
title: "場所をめぐる"
description: "都道府県・エリアから日本のサードプレイスを探す。Third Place Japan 認証店舗の地域別一覧。"
canonical: "/stories/area/"
---
<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">

  <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted mb-12">
    <a href="/stories/" class="hover:text-gold transition-colors">Stories</a>
    <span>／</span>
    <span>場所をめぐる</span>
  </nav>

  <div class="mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
    <p class="label mb-4">場所をめぐる</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-light text-dark mb-4">エリアから探す</h1>
    <div class="gold-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6" data-aos="fade-up">
    {% for pref in areas %}
    <a href="/stories/area/{{ pref.slug }}/"
       class="border border-border p-6 hover:border-gold group transition-colors">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-light text-dark group-hover:text-gold transition-colors mb-2">{{ pref.name }}</h2>
      {% set prefVenues = venues | venuesByArea(pref.slug) %}
      {% if prefVenues.length %}
      <p class="text-xs text-muted">{{ prefVenues.length }}件の認証店舗</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {% for city in pref.cities | head(3) %}
        <span class="text-xs text-muted border border-border px-2 py-0.5">{{ city.name }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</div>
